title: NFL Trade Deadline Recap, Winners/Losers, Andy Dalton BENCHED (Football 10/29)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to break down the lack of moves at the deadline. The guys actually start by discussing a non-trade, but rather the Bengals benching Andy Dalton on his birthday (2:30). They also react to the Bengals, Redskins and Jets failing to make deals (12:15) before issuing trade deadline winners and losers (26:30).
